        {
          "id": "1744cc23d0ad_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "44d5",
          "text": "The Paris Climate Agreement sets an ambitious goal of keeping warming significantly below 2° Celsius (3.6°F). Until now, the global community had agreed to limit global warming to 2 degrees Celsius (3.6 Fahrenheit), in line with the scientific consensus that any warming above that level could lead to catastrophic consequences. But small island nations, which face an existential threat from rising seas, insisted on a more ambitious target of 1.5°C. A compromise was reached, with the global community agreeing to keep warming significantly below 2°C and to pursue “efforts to limit the temperature increase to 1.5 °C.” The goal is to achieve carbon neutrality (a “balance between anthropogenic emissions by sources and removals by sinks of greenhouse gases”) in the second half of this century.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "1744cc23d0ad_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c1a3",
          "text": "Independent from whether we are running out of fossil fuels, it is becoming increasingly clear that we have to stop burning them and find alternative sources of energy based on solar, wind and marine energy sources. The future energy systems are likely to be more decentralised and renewable energy based. This offers a great opportunity for people engaged in the design or retrofitting of sustainable communities and ecovillages. The technologies for decentralised renewable energy systems have evolved a lot and offer viable alternatives financially while reducing environmental impacts significantly and creating more resilience and energy sovereignty.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
